data.description: This remarkable residence, located in the vibrant heart of Colorado Springs, is a true embodiment of fine craftsmanship and thoughtful architecture.  This expansive property offers an abundance of space with seven generously proportioned bedrooms and four contemporary bathrooms — all spread across a substantial 3,119 SqFt of living area. The home features gleaming hardwood floors on the top two levels, creating a warm and welcoming ambiance throughout. For those seeking relaxation, this house provides a unique feature: a dedicated hot tub room, measuring a spacious 12x20. After a long day, unwind by the cozy gas fireplace or retreat to your private hot tub haven. Outdoor lovers will appreciate the sizable covered patio that overlooks nearly a quarter acre of lush greenery, flourishing with grapes and fruit trees. An 18X8 storage shed is also available for all your storage needs. Situated in a tranquil cul-de-sac, the property ensures peace and quiet. The location offers additional perks such as proximity to a Fire Station, ensuring safety is never compromised. Parks are just a stone's throw away, perfect for weekend picnics or evening walks. Schools are nearby, fostering a strong sense of community, and a shopping center is conveniently located just around the corner. The home is equipped with various amenities, including a modern water softener system, an efficient sprinkler system, new roof with 7 year transferable warranty, and RV parking complete with a plug-in. An oversized family room in the basement provides the perfect space for creating cherished memories.
